==Ships to keep==
In general, I like the following types (exceptions do occur):
*WWII survivors, or those who sank in the last few months of the war
*Ships that did not sink during suicide missions such as Ten-Go
*DesDiv 6
*Fallen Angels, serious personalities and quiet/frail girls
*All Allied ships
